      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CANDY STRIDE (1) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish half a length back in second (22.18) at Shepparton in a Grade 5 over 390m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to feature in the finish again. SIR STARBUCK (2) turned in a plain performance last time when seventh at Warrnambool over 390m behind Genesis Bale (22.82) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. Shapes as one to consider. DAVE (4) was a last-start winner from box one at Warrnambool over 390m (22.11) after leading through, scoring by 3 lengths. Leading player again. PAW XYLA (3) has been in the frame at her last two runs, most recently when third (24.34) in a Grade 5 over 425m at Bendigo.",
